Name: Very High
Earthquake Hazard: Site has a 2% in 50 year PGA value greater than 59.5 and Liquefaction greater than Low to Moderate.

Name: High
Earthquake Hazard: Site has a 2% in 50 year PGA value greater than 59.9 or a 2% in 50 year PGA greater than 29.5 and Liquefaction greater than Low to Moderate.

Name: Moderate
Earthquake Hazard: Site has a 2% in 50 year PGA value greater than 29.5 or a 2% in 50 year PGA greater than 19.5 and Liquefaction greater than Low to Moderate.

Name: Low
Earthquake Hazard: Site has a 2% in 50 year PGA value less than 19.5 and a Liquefaction less than moderate.
